from external.

00:14:22.400 --> 00:14:25.150
And insulin is housed
in the pancreas.

00:14:25.150 --> 00:14:27.190
And it promotes satiety.

00:14:27.190 --> 00:14:32.070
It is anorexigenic. eugenics
So orexigenic, anorexigenic.

00:14:32.070 --> 00:14:34.270
Anorexigenic is the
