It fires, and it
communicates information

00:15:57.130 --> 00:15:59.690
about what I'm supposed to do.

00:15:59.690 --> 00:16:02.990
So people that travele down this
lane of the brain or this lane

00:16:02.990 --> 00:16:06.700
down the highway, they
get an anorexigenic signal

00:16:06.700 --> 00:16:07.660
to their brain.

00:16:07.660 --> 00:16:11.530
They have high levels of what's
called BDNF, which is brain

00:16:11.530 --> 00:16:13.450
derived neurotrophic factor.

00:16:13.450 --> 00:16:16.540
And for these people that travel
down this lane or this pathway

00:16:16.540 --> 00:16:19.620
in the brain, they
tend to be very lean.

