00:17:22.170 --> 00:17:26.010
but no matter what they do,
they seem to defend a higher set

00:17:26.010 --> 00:17:29.110
point, it's a high likelihood
that they have a predilection

00:17:29.110 --> 00:17:31.810
to firing down this
pathway of the brain.

00:17:31.810 --> 00:17:32.860
And it's unfair.

00:17:32.860 --> 00:17:34.690
We want to do with
